   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>LIFE-STUDY OF JEREMIAH MESSAGE TEN ISRAEL'S SIN AGAINST JEHOVAH</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>AND</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>JEHOVAH'S PUNISHMENT UPON ISRAEL 4 ISRAEL'S HYPOCRITICAL WORSHIP TO JEHOVAH 1 Scripture Reading: Jer 7 10</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>In this message on Israel's sin against Jehovah and Jehovah's punishment upon Israel, we will begin to consider Israel's hypocritical worship to Jehovah.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>I. ISRAEL'S ACTUALLY JUDAH'S HYPOCRITICAL</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>WORSHIP TO JEHOVAH THEIR GOD A. A Worship of Superstition</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Israel's actually Judah's 7:21; 9:26 hypocritical worship to Jehovah their God was a false worship and was a worship of superstition.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>1.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Trusting in the Words of Falsehood</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>concerning the Temple of Jehovah</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>In their superstitious worship, Israel trusted in the words of falsehood that said, "The temple of Jehovah, the temple of Jehovah, these buildings are the temple of Jehovah" 7:4 .</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>To them even the temple had become an idol and something of superstition.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Thus, Jeremiah told them not to say these words regarding the temple of Jehovah.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>2.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Doing Many Wicked Things</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>and Then Coming and Standing before Jehovah</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>and Saying That They Would Be Delivered</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>On the one hand, the people of Israel worshipped God; on the other hand, they were given to stealing, murdering, committing adultery, swearing falsely, burning incense to Baal, and going after other gods.</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>After doing such things, they would come and stand before Jehovah in the house which is called by His name and say, "We are delivered!" vv.</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>9-10 .</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>By saying this they were deceiving themselves and cheating themselves.</S>
   </TEXT>
